{"tid":1563583,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"9.15 轉戰各區商場有冇得諗","createTime":"2019-09-12T12:39:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T13:39:05.000Z","uid":176427,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e5c2b36116a5a88c8e6c3f11febb7f49403e9003","tid":1563583,"uid":176427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T12:39:21.000Z","msg":"應對黑警成日都出反對通知書<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1563429\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1563429</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n頭先睇完其他巴打嘅comment，覺得會唔會有轉戰商場嘅可能性呢？遊行作用係曬馬，話俾政府同全世界知道，即使佢地滿足咗一個訴求，市民仍然係非常不滿，堅持五大訴求。<br />\n<br />\n但大家見到上幾次遊行，政府已經同黨鐵合作，下下都封站之後大搜捕，拉咗唔少手足。咁樣落去只會愈拉愈多人。所以既然15號遊行出咗反對通知書，我地會唔會將計就計，好似85罷工咁去各區商場呢？就好似平日，又聚到人，又相對安全。<br />\n<br />\n求意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8500910fc1525529faedcded8e80bd697f068777","tid":1563583,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T12:40:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"c054da677f9e29e15f463c37e9fea2f11f234ad0","tid":1563583,"uid":121713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T12:57:54.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" 